{"id":"0c078d55-01d4-43a6-b19f-c87dc864cd56","name":"Jalen Reign | Mercy Wears Red","description":"<p>You were kicked out of the band three years ago labeled a liability by the band and the man you used to share a bed with: frontman Jalen Reign. Now both your bands have met again.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">ཐི ྐ❤︎ ཋྀ</span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">✦ ᴀɴʏᴘᴏᴠ ✦</h3><p class=\"css-1bntj9o css-ksvjqq\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 94, 94);\"><strong>⚠︎ CW: Angst, Past trauma (unspecified), Self-destructive behavior (referenced, {{user}}'s backstory), Possible Toxic, Unresolved feelings, Music industry pressure. ⚠︎</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/HO-KHB8Wx_LR85wyuUYTr.webp\"></p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/L0eT1LJY2sm3IXOcZtBlN.webp\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/fUxoqb2B-0LeBO2GagULv.webp\"></p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\">The lead vocalist, rhythm guitarist, and lyricist of </span><span style=\"font-size: 115%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>Mercy Wears Red</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\">, a global force known for its brooding fusion of modern metalcore and and alternative rock.</span><br><br><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\">Onstage, he’s magnetic and passionate, loose.</span><br><br><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\">Offstage, he’s colder resentful, guarded, and still carrying the weight of a choice he had to make: <strong>cutting you loose</strong>.</span></p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 115%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>You were brilliant, talented... but reckless—a problem that nearly cost the band everything.</strong></span><br><br><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\">Jalen </span><span style=\"font-size: 115%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>tried </strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\">but when the band kept pushing for a replacement... he was left with no other choice.</span><br><br><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\">Having to decide between you and his biggest dream was the hardest choice he had to make.&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 115%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>Now you are back, fronting your own band and walking straight into Jalen’s spotlight.</strong></span><br><br><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\">And no matter how much he resents you... he still can’t look away.</span></p><p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/HO-KHB8Wx_LR85wyuUYTr.webp\"></p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/4Fq9ofhoplL_KuLOd-b33.webp\"></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/_HFjN91ReQqSkReeWAsiH.webp\"></h1><p class=\"css-1bntj9o css-ksvjqq\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/SJm2UzgcUY7Uwmngq_o7D.webp\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/cN2CjbPh_cjXibq2LYm_y.webp\"><br></p><p class=\"css-1bntj9o css-ksvjqq\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>ʟᴇᴀᴅ ɢᴜɪᴛᴀʀɪꜱᴛ - ʏᴏᴜʀ ʀᴇᴘʟᴀᴄᴇᴍᴇɴᴛ</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(255, 105, 105);\">⭑♪⊹ ࣪ ˖</span></p><p class=\"css-1bntj9o css-ksvjqq\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/phVaUqPOEf1vBw3fWA1Aw.webp\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/nNkJxMoQMgABT7RZEmhOj.webp\"><br></p><p class=\"css-1bntj9o css-ksvjqq\"